title: DG Strategic Plans Division calls on FM
content:
ISLAMABAD, Sep 2 (APP): Director General Strategic Plans Division (SPD) called on Foreign Minister Shah Mahmood Qureshi at the Ministry of Foreign Affairs here on Wednesday.
The DG SPD updated the Foreign Minister about the performance of the division.
The Foreign Minister lauded the role played by SPD relating to strategic and tactical domain.
